---
layout: base.njk
title: Welcome to Electron Workshop - Home
permalink: "/"
---

{# ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="py-4 pb-5 mb-5 border-bottom border-2">
  <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-7 col-lg-8">
      <p class="text-primary fw-bold text-uppercase mb-2" style="letter-spacing:.08em; font-size:.8rem;">Electron Workshop</p>
      <h1 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-3 lh-sm">Building the open tech commons, together</h1>
      <p class="lead text-secondary mb-4">A meeting ground for community organisers, ecosystem thinkers, and open innovators. Through global awareness festivals, community gatherings, open sprints, and network collaboration — we help each other thrive.</p>
      <div class="d-flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
        <a href="/calendar/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">See What's On</a>
        <a href="/connect/" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg">Get Involved</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-5 col-lg-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
      <img src="/assets/images/logo.jpg" alt="Electron Workshop" class="img-fluid rounded" style="max-height: 150px; object-fit: contain;">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── FEATURED EVENT ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
{% set hasFeatured = false %}
{% for card in homeCards %}
  {% if card.featured == true and card.display != false %}{% set hasFeatured = true %}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if hasFeatured %}
<section class="mb-5">
  <p class="text-primary fw-bold text-uppercase mb-3" style="letter-spacing:.08em; font-size:.8rem;"><i class="bi bi-star-fill me-1"></i>Featured</p>
  {% for card in homeCards %}
    {% if card.featured == true and card.display != false %}
      <div class="card border-primary border-2 shadow overflow-hidden">
        {% if card.banner %}
          <div class="overflow-hidden" style="max-height: 260px;">
            <img src="{{ card.banner }}" alt="{{ card.title }}" class="w-100" style="object-fit: cover; width: 100%;">
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between align-items-center gap-3 p-4">
          <div>
            <h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-1">{{ card.title }}</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary mb-2 text-preline">{{ card.text }}</p>
            {% if card.tags %}
              <div>
                {% for tag in card.tags %}
                  <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-25 text-primary me-1">#{{ tag }}</span>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          {% if card.href and card.button %}
            <a href="{{ card.href }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg flex-shrink-0">{{ card.button }}</a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</section>
{% endif %}

{# ── HOW WE WORK (The Fabric) ──────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="mb-4">
  <h2 class="fs-3 fw-semibold mb-1 border-bottom border-2 border-primary d-inline-block">How We Work</h2>
  <p class="text-secondary mb-4">Three interlocking threads that together form a fabric for the open tech commons.</p>
  <div class="row g-4">

    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-primary border-opacity-25 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <i class="bi bi-calendar-event fs-2 text-primary flex-shrink-0"></i>
            <h3 class="h5 mb-0">Festivals &amp; Gatherings</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-secondary flex-grow-1">Global awareness festivals — Software Freedom Day, Hardware Freedom Day, Document Freedom Day, Linux Birthday — set the themes and focus for the year. Around them, and around major local conferences, we run <strong>chainferences</strong> and our flagship <strong>Un-forum</strong>: a home for conversations that don't have one elsewhere.</p>
          <a href="/calendar/" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm mt-2 align-self-start">View Calendar</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-primary border-opacity-25 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge fs-2 text-primary flex-shrink-0"></i>
            <h3 class="h5 mb-0">Electron Sprints</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-secondary flex-grow-1">Fortnightly open work sessions using self-hosted tools. Community and open projects make real progress while people learn skills, make friends, and contribute to a cause. Work and community woven together — no burnout, just doing.</p>
          <a href="/initiatives/sprints/" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm mt-2 align-self-start">Join a Sprint</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-primary border-opacity-25 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <i class="bi bi-diagram-3 fs-2 text-primary flex-shrink-0"></i>
            <h3 class="h5 mb-0">Electron Network</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-secondary flex-grow-1">Community groups joining forces. Shared capacity, collective intelligence, and coordinated action — activating audiences for causes in the open innovation commons. Stronger together than apart.</p>
          <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm mt-2 align-self-start">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{# ── AWARENESS CALENDAR ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
{% if awarenessdays.length %}
<section class="mb-5 mt-4">
  <p class="text-primary fw-bold text-uppercase mb-2" style="letter-spacing:.08em; font-size:.8rem;"><i class="bi bi-globe me-1"></i>Global Awareness Festivals</p>
  <p class="text-secondary small mb-3">These festivals set our themes and focus across the year — days the open tech movement celebrates worldwide.</p>
  <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
    {% for day in awarenessdays %}
      <a href="{{ day.href }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-decoration-none">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 rounded border border-primary border-opacity-25 bg-body-tertiary">
          <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-25 text-primary" style="font-size:.7rem;">{{ day.month }}</span>
          <i class="bi {{ day.icon }} text-primary small"></i>
          <span class="small fw-semibold text-dark">{{ day.title }}</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{# ── WHAT'S ON ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
{% set hasEvents = false %}
{% for card in homeCards %}
  {% if (card.cardType == "chainference" or card.cardType == "whatsOnEcosystem") and card.display != false and card.featured != true %}
    {% set hasEvents = true %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if hasEvents %}
<section class="mt-4 mb-5">
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
    <h2 class="fs-3 fw-semibold mb-0 border-bottom border-2 border-primary d-inline-block">What's On</h2>
    <a href="/calendar/" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">Full calendar <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></a>
  </div>
  <div class="row g-4">
    {% for card in homeCards %}
      {% if (card.cardType == "chainference" or card.cardType == "whatsOnEcosystem") and card.display != false and card.featured != true %}
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
          <div class="card h-100 border-primary border-opacity-25 shadow-sm border-primary-hover">

            {% if card.banner %}
              <div class="card-img-top overflow-hidden" style="aspect-ratio: 3/1;">
                <img src="{{ card.banner }}" alt="{{ card.title }}" class="w-100 h-100 object-fit-cover">
              </div>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
              <div class="d-flex align-items-start justify-content-between gap-2 mb-2">
                <div class="flex-grow-1">
                  {% if card.cardType == "chainference" %}
                    <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-25 text-primary mb-1">Chainference</span>
                  {% endif %}
                  <p class="h5 mb-0">{{ card.title }}</p>
                </div>
                {% if card.logo %}
                  <img src="{{ card.logo }}" alt="{{ card.title }} logo"
                      class="img-fluid flex-shrink-0"
                      style="max-height: 36px; width: auto; object-fit: contain;">
                {% endif %}
              </div>

              {% if card.tags %}
                <div class="mb-2">
                  {% for tag in card.tags %}
                    <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary me-1 mb-1">#{{ tag }}</span>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              <p class="text-secondary text-preline flex-grow-1">{{ card.text }}</p>

              {% if card.href and card.button %}
                <a href="{{ card.href }}" class="btn btn-primary stretched-link mt-auto align-self-start">{{ card.button }}</a>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{# ── OFFERINGS STRIP ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="mb-5">
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
    <h2 class="fs-3 fw-semibold mb-0 border-bottom border-2 border-primary d-inline-block">What We Offer</h2>
    <a href="/offering/" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">View all <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></a>
  </div>
  <div class="row g-3">
    {% for item in offerings %}
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
        <a href="/offering/{{ item.slug }}/" class="text-decoration-none">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded border border-primary border-opacity-25 h-100 border-primary-hover bg-white">
            {% if item.logo %}
              <img src="{{ item.logo }}" alt="{{ item.title }} logo" style="width: 32px; height: 32px; object-fit: contain; flex-shrink: 0;">
            {% else %}
              <i class="bi bi-tools fs-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0"></i>
            {% endif %}
            <p class="fw-semibold text-dark mb-0 small lh-sm">{{ item.title }}</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{# ── PARTNERS / LOGOS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="mt-5 mb-4">
  <div class="row g-3 align-items-center justify-content-center">
    {% for groupName, logos in homeLogos %}

    <div class="mt-5 text-center">
      <h4 class="border-bottom border-2 border-primary d-inline-block">{{ groupName }}</h4>
    </div>

      {% for logo in logos %}
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-auto">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center p-3" style="min-height: 80px;">
            <img src="{{ logo.src }}"
                alt="{{ logo.alt }}"
                class="img-fluid opacity-75 hover-opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                style="max-height: 60px; max-width: 100%; object-fit: contain; width:100%">
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}

    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>


</div> {# Close the container from base.njk #}

{# ── GET INVOLVED ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
{% set hasEngage = false %}
{% for card in homeCards %}
  {% if card.cardType == "engage" %}{% set hasEngage = true %}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if hasEngage %}
  <div class="gear-transition" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <section class="py-5 bg-primary">
    <div class="container mt-5">
      <h2 class="fs-3 fw-normal mb-1 border-bottom border-2 border-white d-inline-block text-white">Get Involved</h2>
      <p class="text-white opacity-75 mb-4">There are different ways to participate — pick the one that fits you.</p>
      <div class="row g-4">
        {% for card in homeCards %}
          {% if card.cardType == "engage" and card.display != false %}
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
              <div class="card h-100 bg-white border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    {% if card.icon %}
                      <i class="bi {{ card.icon }} fs-3 text-primary flex-shrink-0"></i>
                    {% endif %}
                    <p class="h5 mb-0 text-primary">{{ card.title }}</p>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mb-4 text-secondary text-preline">{{ card.text }}</p>
                  {% if card.href and card.button %}
                    <a href="{{ card.href }}" class="btn btn-outline-primary stretched-link">{{ card.button }}</a>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endif %}

<div class="container"> {# Reopen the container for any content that follows #}
